rows.label: bf04160100_0010
rows.name: Ohhhh! You that old Muimui guy?

rows.label: bf04160100_0020
rows.name:
Of course Tora remember!
Muimui should have said to start with.

rows.label: bf04160100_0030
rows.name: ...Muimui did say.

rows.label: bf04160100_0040
rows.name:
Oh, right! Muimui not very interesting,
so Tora forgot he exist.

rows.label: bf04160100_0050
rows.name: Tora! That's not very nice.

rows.label: bf04160100_0060
rows.name: No no, I do not blame Tora.

rows.label: bf04160100_0070
rows.name:
Tora-san was very young back then.
Not surprising he forget.

rows.label: bf04160100_0080
rows.name: Besides, Masterpon was quite distracted just now.

rows.label: bf04160100_0085
rows.name: Only thinking of how to upgrade Hana.

rows.label: bf04160100_0090
rows.name:
My, this is...
An artificial Blade, isn't it, meh?

rows.label: bf04160100_0100
rows.name:
That's right! Based on the blueprints
my grandpa and dad left behind.

rows.label: bf04160100_0110
rows.name: Tora completed it!

rows.label: bf04160100_0120
rows.name: Meh meh... How wonderful...

rows.label: bf04160100_0130
rows.name:
If only Professor Senzo still here
to see results of hard work!

rows.label: bf04160100_0140
rows.name: Muimui, you have any idea where Dad went?

rows.label: bf04160100_0150
rows.name: That day, when the lab was attacked...

rows.label: bf04160100_0160
rows.name:
Muimui was out on errand. When I got back,
Professor Senzo's body was lying there.

rows.label: bf04160100_0170
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf04160100_0180
rows.name: But there was no sign of Professor Tatezo.

rows.label: bf04160100_0190
rows.name: I see... Even Muimui not know...

rows.label: bf04160100_0200
rows.name:
Do not feel down, Masterpon.
We will find Dad someday.

rows.label: bf04160100_0210
rows.name: Though no evidence for this hypothesis.

rows.label: bf04160100_0220
rows.name:
Anyway, Muimui apologize for interrupting
your trip when you just arrived in city.

rows.label: bf04160100_0230
rows.name: Friend of Muimui run an inn just up ahead.

rows.label: bf04160100_0240
rows.name:
Place with famous hot springs. If you
like, Muimui can try to get you discount!

rows.label: bf04160100_0250
rows.name: Muimui is best friend!
